<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;">2月23<span style="list-style-type: none; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">日，由赣南科技学院副校长左群教授为组长，南昌师范学院马克思主义学院党总支书记肖良平教授、江西理工大学商学院党政办主任岳中心副教授、江西财经大学会计学院陈青副教授、江西省教育厅张文瑞副研究员为组员的省教育厅民办高校年检与综合考核工作专家组一行</span>5人来校开展实地核查工作，全面检查指导学校2023年度各项工作，并在学校<span style="list-style-type: none; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">创客大厦</span><span style="list-style-type: none; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">第一会议室召开座谈会。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">学校理事长陈方平，党委书记、督导专员江延湖，校长庄力可，执行校长范红铭及全体校领导出席座谈会。各职能部门负责人，二级学院院长、书记，审计机构代表和师生代表参加会议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A14%3A38IMG_9205.jpg?Expires=2024097279&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=9SVUiwOqquaIVDxPKksU%2FlwR%2F18%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="list-style-type: none; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">左群教授主持会议并讲话。他介绍了专家组成员，详细说明了年检与综合考核工作的依据、内容、核查方式和流程安排。他提出几点工作要求：一是安排适当数量工作人员及相关职能部门负责人配合开展核查工作，及时提供相关材料，介绍相关情况，并就工作组成员提出的有关问题作出说明；二是学校要严格落实中央八项规定精神，全力配合工作组完成本次年检与综合考核工作</span><span style="list-style-type: none; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A16%3A16IMG_9200.jpg?Expires=2024097377&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=hvUbKY4xrHrN936qfGE2awoUkm8%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">陈方平代表校理事会、校党委、校行政对专家组一行的到来表示热烈欢迎和衷心感谢，并表示，自学校开展职业本科教育工作以来，学校始终坚持职业教育的属性，紧密结合地方产业，实施产教融合、科教融汇战略，走产学研用发展之路，立足江西、辐射全国，面向软件行业，为培育德智体美劳全面发展、适应区域经济社会需要、掌握本专业的基本理论知识和职业技能、能在相应的行业企业从事实际工作的高素质高层次技术技能人才而努力奋斗。此次专家组来校实地核查是对学校把脉问诊和关心帮助，学校将积极配合、认真学习、不断进步。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A17%3A59IMG_9209.jpg?Expires=2024097479&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=GIS26joPXYJyRA5TBjEGdwppjxc%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 40px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 41px;text-align: justify"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">庄力可从主要成绩、基本情况和需要改进的地方三个方面汇报了学校</span>2023年度年检和综合考核工作组织实施情况及自查自评情况。他表示，过去一年，学校在坚持党的教育方针与依法治校方面、办学条件和资源持续优化方面、办学质量和办学水平不断提高方面、办学声誉办学特色成效显著方面都取得良好成绩。未来，学校将以更加饱满的热情、更加务实的作风，迎接未来的挑战，为学校的健康稳定、高质量发展而努力工作，为江西高质量发展贡献力量。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 40px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 41px;text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 40px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A19%3A33IMG_9214.jpg?Expires=2024097573&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Psjwegj8IPdAM8NCvkP%2BIkRKmcM%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-size: 16px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px 1px;padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;vertical-align: baseline;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;line-height: 40px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-indent: 41px;text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;">座谈会后，专家组通过查阅资料、实地考察、访谈相关负责人、师生线上座谈等方式，深入细致地核查了学校党建和思政工作、办学条件、依法治校、办学行为、财务与资产管理、师生权益保障等工作，仔细检查了学校年检材料，并就相关工作提出意见和建议。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A21%3A33IMG_9236_wps%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.jpg?Expires=2024097694&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=xgzB3Z3ivO0x3%2FBFLvQ%2BBjl0hgI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0em; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px !important; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-02-24%2009%3A22%3A42IMG_9246_wps%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.jpg?Expires=2024097762&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=y3KP7nA%2Byj%2B3Co6RV%2Fq0eMKkd88%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box;border: 0px;vertical-align: baseline;padding: 0px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;list-style-type: none;-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;filter: saturate(1.1);display: block"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 41px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 